Here is the original nabble thread: http://qooxdoo.678.n2.nabble.com/Grid-layout-CellWidget-exclusion-and-spacingY-problem-td6778693.html

After a quick look in the Grid Layout Script, I noticed it finally works if we change the line 1320:

top += rowHeights[row] + vSpacing;

by:

top += rowHeights[row];

Maybe it&#39;s not the only place to change but it looks then OK.

